Interface Item

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FormattableElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ItemExtender, ItemImpl

    public interface Item
extends FormattableElement
    A representation of the model object 'Item'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Parent
    • Children
    • Policy
    • Param Object
    • Param EObject
